name: FIND THE TREASURE!
description:
the Fourth in the series featuring Jumba, continues where "TAKE A REST!" leaves off. Jumba, the much-loved character from the "JUMBA LOVE COSPLAYS" NFT project, has finished his robot that he and his crew plan to take to the moon.
"FIND THE TREASURE!"
